actions.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment and with a preamble by Voice Vote.

official_title: A resolution to authorize the Senate Financial Clerk and other present and former Senate employees to testify in the case of United States v. Darrell A. Tomblin, et al.

summary.text: Authorizes Stuart F. Balderson, the Senate Financial Clerk, and other present and former Senate employees to testify and produce records in the case of United States v. Darrell A. Tomblin, et al.

titles.title: A resolution to authorize the Senate Financial Clerk and other present and former Senate employees to testify in the case of United States v. Darrell A. Tomblin, et al.
